Jiaxing Dibeisi Electroacoustics Co., Ltd.
Company Overview
Situated in the Yangtze River Delta, the northeast part of Zhejiang Province, which is the place with the most economic vigor in China, Jiaxing Dibeisi Electroacoustics Co., Ltd. is close to Shanghai-Hangzhou Expressway, adjacent to Shanghai in the east and Hangzhou in the west. We are only 120km away from Shanghai Pudong International Airport, 90km away from Hangzhou International Airport and 110km away from Shanghai Port, enjoying convenient transportation.Our company specializes in manufacturing speakers for cars or stage use, car cabinets and stage speaker cabinets. Our annual output is 4.5 million pieces of various loudspeakers and over 500000 sets of car and stage cabinets. With 28 years experience in producing electroacoustic products, first-class scientists and technicians and advanced manufacturing and inspection equipment, our company has lot of newly created products with our own knowledge property rights. Our company is willing to provide OEM and ODM products for customers from at home and abroad. "Quality the first, reputation above all" is our principle. We are sincerely supplying high quality products for domestic and foreign customers, and offering good after-sales services. Every customer will come happily and return satisfactorily.
